          }
        },
        "text_XfUr34": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Apollo embodies the quintessential American Dream, with its founders hailing from Europe as first-generation immigrants. The journey of Apollo began in 2013 when a group of co-founders, who were previously involved with the wholesale brand Vaporize101, embarked on their own venture in the realm of portable dry herb vaporizers. Apollo was born out of the passion of a team of vape enthusiasts driven by the vision to provide affordable luxury within the dry herb vape market. They aimed to fill the gap left by overpriced high-end vaporizers that lacked the bold design elements found in other consumer electronics.</p>"
          }
        }
